{"tid":2446713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎明來到 要光復 這香港","createTime":"2021-03-14T16:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T22:41:43.000Z","uid":105691,"like":39,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0e9f795619ae44b33af31e49be55a71740b63d44","tid":2446713,"uid":105691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6356614b95f1497ba903d05b8e4339a46fd2fcdd","tid":2446713,"uid":226955,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:10:03.000Z","msg":"樓主切記初心不可動搖<br />\n<br />\n共匪就係想佢統治下嘅社會道德敗壞，人人互不信任，自自然然就唔會團結得起嚟反抗極權，所以共匪會致力於敗壞原來社會道德，例子有毀滅傳統文化入面有關道德嘅觀念，扭曲教育同媒體，以考試功名同茶餘飯後娛樂全方位日以繼夜咁洗你腦，令你變得自私，除咗政府之外對其他人表現得猜疑，而導人為善嘅宗教亦好自然受到波及，原有教善被扭曲成為極權思想服務，呢點支那大把例子唔洗再點提，以<span class=\"red\">叢林法則嘅觀念植入每一個人心底裡</span>，人人自私自利，正如今日嘅支那社會，篤灰文化盛行，街上見人有難唔會有人幫手，道德敗壞至此，政權就穩如泰山。<span class=\"red\">而五毛就跟住呢個指令去為極權散佈呢種思想，逐步逐步敗壞成個社會嘅道德同對未來嘅希望。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">Anyway 大家要學識喺充滿負能量嘅氣氛之下，仍然保持當初嘅信念，控制到自己一直努力嘅目標方向，極權就係要成個社會心灰意冷，最好就係個個「覺得做乜都冇用啦」呢種思想深入民心，自自然然道德觀念崩潰，民間團結唔到，極權政府就可以不費成本而高枕無憂。</span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n以下係理論層面去解釋我上面嘅說話：（摘錄自高學歷巴打post）<br />\n<br />\n1970年，蘇聯KGB特工Yuri Bezmenov叛變（無中譯，Google譯做 尤里&middot;貝茲諾夫），投靠美國，並公開蘇聯情報部門顛覆敵對國家社會嘅方法。由意志崩壞（demoralisation）開始，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>令到整個社會感到無助，唔團結，冷感，撕裂，以致崩潰，不戰而敗。</strong></span></span>呢套理論有學名，叫「顛覆」Subversion，而達到顛覆嘅行爲，就叫做 active measures / активные мероприятия。<br />\n<br />\n2019年，中華人民共和國依舊行使同一套理論，務求不需派兵嘅情況之下，摧毀香港。<br />\n<br />\nSubversion有四個步驟：demoralisation破壞意志+道德，destabilisation社會動盪，crisis災難點，normalisation正常化。<br />\n<br />\n以下係英文原版，RedDragon1會員詳盡中文譯本<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeVyEwJMdEQDTTxmeiJhXDLBPChrZSqCD7desS9xer9TZ?filename=mv5bmV1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmv5bmV1.png&h=e1116adf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcQpKGz3ABebBrQwoqsFrGwcYd25tgePiY4EEXPMVKUJ2?filename=yM38o9n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyM38o9n.png&h=00bad446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUxiyh8foWrdAynRe87kbFYqKpm8GfyLAUDAoEeEm1qzx?filename=EvWRmV3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEvWRmV3.png&h=b10ab2c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdVxvDtzTsUJjEmvyAt7TrH8V1JsBVyPrJbMmm9GUgdUd?filename=CMfZvPo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCMfZvPo.png&h=32ead5cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個圖最後兩個顛覆步驟冇講清楚：<br />\n<br />\n「Crisis災難點」係指令到社會運作嘅機器失效，即係銀行停止發票，立法會停止會議，法院不能夠再審判。同時間，另類政府組織會冒起，如人民法院。<br />\n<br />\n「Crisis災難點」未直接入「Normalisation正常化」之前有可能會走兩條路：國際介入（多國戰爭），or內戰。但係如果冇呢兩樣嘢發生嘅話，就會直接入最後一步：<br />\n<br />\n「Normalisation正常化」，係指「社會動盪被入侵者完全制止」，蘇聯嘅例子係俄羅斯坦克車入城，將原本親蘇聯嘅內奸、政客殺哂（因爲已經冇利用價值），由外來嘅俄羅斯人清洗一切反抗聲音，「正常化」個動盪。"},{"pid":"7fd7485292b1355e4b7977d755cb62d0bfab5a46","tid":2446713,"uid":39780,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:10:27.000Z","msg":"shi"},{"pid":"6921292d7c6cba5611e58a3c8bb12b6ef82d5a9a","tid":2446713,"uid":39780,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7fd7485292b1355e4b7977d755cb62d0bfab5a46","tid":2446713,"uid":39780,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:10:27.000Z","msg":"shi"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:10:44.000Z","msg":"Chong"},{"pid":"5ebf13e894fe117da9293f081ca3a803717ede44","tid":2446713,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c70fe686642e873b644ab6173d80c780b4fb29","tid":2446713,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:13:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c813b9da789a4740ee570936ff19a8cdfe5cf82","tid":2446713,"uid":12558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:13:50.000Z","msg":"同行兒女　為正義　時代革命"},{"pid":"c880eb879d640d95b05b7f7a863e7f09947f582f","tid":2446713,"uid":139228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:15:20.000Z","msg":"黎明幾時被秋後算賬？"},{"pid":"5c56a866ce9a4a4b09d41bb2c5dde9d35dab24df","tid":2446713,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710bfe4ff516b0a4f85cc594184aff0857747235","tid":2446713,"uid":105691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c813b9da789a4740ee570936ff19a8cdfe5cf82","tid":2446713,"uid":12558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:13:50.000Z","msg":"同行兒女　為正義　時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:26:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd2520cb6f943409514801d7c50a2b8b0dae0d1","tid":2446713,"uid":46072,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:28:24.000Z","msg":"祈求民主與自由"},{"pid":"2f1ee2004cc18f954f236994ee6020368181e701","tid":2446713,"uid":314767,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:29:41.000Z","msg":"萬世都不朽"},{"pid":"4e7f60504c62291e9d322868cd6c8e6b0892611b","tid":2446713,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:40:54.000Z","msg